<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 01:06:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧盟各国政府面临对中国电动汽车关税的关键投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-face-pivotal-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟成员国周五面临关键投票，决定是否对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达 45% 的关税，这是欧盟最引人注目的贸易案件，这可能会遭到北京方面的报复。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 01:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-face-pivotal-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国的刺激措施吸引投资者重返陷入困境的房地产行业的离岸债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stimulus-draws-investors-back-offshore-bonds-troubled-property-sector-2024-10-03/</link><description>一些中国和全球机构投资者正在重新审视中国房地产债券，押注随着政府加快努力促进经济增长并重振陷入债务危机的房地产行业，前景将有所改善。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 23:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stimulus-draws-investors-back-offshore-bonds-troubled-property-sector-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：石油对世界市场的阴影变暗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 21:50:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度与美国签署关键电池矿物供应链合作协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-us-cooperate-critical-battery-minerals-trade-minister-says-2024-10-03/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔和美国商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多周四签署了一项协议，合作加强两国电动汽车和清洁能源应用中使用的锂、钴和其他关键矿物的供应链。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 19:53:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-us-cooperate-critical-battery-minerals-trade-minister-says-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>向美国东海岸港口发货数量最多的零售商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-with-highest-number-shipments-into-us-east-coast-ports-2024-10-03/</link><description>美国东海岸港口近五十年来最大规模的码头工人罢工已进入第三天，威胁到从香蕉到汽车零部件等货物的短缺，并导致停泊在主要港口外的船舶积压。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-with-highest-number-shipments-into-us-east-coast-ports-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：西班牙呼吁在欧盟就电动汽车关税进行投票之前与中国妥协</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/spain-calls-compromise-with-china-ahead-eu-vote-ev-tariffs-2024-10-03/</link><description>西班牙周四在欧盟就电动汽车关税进行关键投票前夕表示，欧盟应寻求与中国达成妥协和谈判结果。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:20:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/spain-calls-compromise-with-china-ahead-eu-vote-ev-tariffs-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，德国将投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-vehicles-sources-say-2024-10-03/</link><description>知情人士周四告诉路透社，德国周五将投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-vehicles-sources-say-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，在线零售商 Shein 将在伦敦 IPO 前不久举行路演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-retailer-shein-hold-roadshows-soon-ahead-london-ipo-sources-say-2024-10-03/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，Shein 将在未来几周内为其计划的伦敦首次公开募股 (IPO) 举行非正式投资者会议，在等待英国监管机构批准的同时推进准备工作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 15:14:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-retailer-shein-hold-roadshows-soon-ahead-london-ipo-sources-say-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>德国工会和汽车工人呼吁德国投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-union-auto-workers-call-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-10-03/</link><description>德国强大的工会IG Metall和德国主要汽车制造商的员工代表周四在一份声明中表示，德国应该投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:35:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-union-auto-workers-call-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>世界银行启动新的商业环境调查，匈牙利、爱沙尼亚、新加坡名列前茅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-bank-launches-new-business-climate-survey-with-hungary-estonia-singapore-2024-10-03/</link><description>世界银行周四对 50 个经济体推出了修改后的商业和投资环境调查，匈牙利、爱沙尼亚和新加坡在三个类别中名列前茅，旨在避免导致世界银行取消丑闻缠身的“营商环境”排名的问题。 2021 年。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-bank-launches-new-business-climate-survey-with-hungary-estonia-singapore-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称与西方的对抗是历史上前所未有的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-says-confrontation-with-west-is-unparalleled-history-2024-10-03/</link><description>周四，一名俄罗斯高级外交官在被问及与 1962 年古巴导弹危机的比较时表示，目前俄罗斯与西方国家在乌克兰问题上的对抗史无前例，一个错误就可能导致灾难。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-says-confrontation-with-west-is-unparalleled-history-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>解说：欧盟调查中国制造的电动汽车接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-happens-next-china-made-evs-investigated-by-eu-2024-10-03/</link><description>欧盟成员国将于周五就欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的提案进行投票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-happens-next-china-made-evs-investigated-by-eu-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官表示，Stellantis与雷诺合并的传言“纯粹是猜测”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/rumours-stellantis-renault-merger-are-pure-speculation-says-stellantis-ceo-2024-10-03/</link><description>Stellantis 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 周四在参观这家法国-意大利汽车制造商位于法国东部的中心之一时表示，有关 Stellantis 和雷诺合并的传言“纯粹是猜测”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:12:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/rumours-stellantis-renault-merger-are-pure-speculation-says-stellantis-ceo-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利外交部长将否决欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-will-veto-eu-plan-impose-chinese-ev-tariffs-foreign-minister-2024-10-03/</link><description>匈牙利外交部长彼得·西雅尔托(Peter Szijjarto)周四在其Facebook页面上表示，匈牙利将否决一项欧盟提议，该提议旨在对中国制造的电动汽车(EV)进口征收高达45%的关税，因为该计划“有害且危险”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:40:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-will-veto-eu-plan-impose-chinese-ev-tariffs-foreign-minister-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾严肃对待外国在该国从事间谍活动的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-takes-allegations-foreign-spying-country-seriously-2024-10-03/</link><description>菲律宾周四对媒体报道称外国在该国进行秘密行动表示担忧，并表示正在与相关机构协调解决此事。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-takes-allegations-foreign-spying-country-seriously-2024-10-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>